# Teknovo Product Rule

## DO

- Read **Master PRD** (`docs/prd/master/master-prd.md`) and module PRDs under `docs/prd/` before implementation
- Resolve document priority per `AGENTS.md`: ADR â†’ PRD â†’ Database â†’ API â†’ RBAC â†’ Design System â†’ Coding Standard
- Break work into **modules** with clear boundaries, ownership, and verification steps
- Run workflow gates in order: **Taste â†’ Assurance Sign-Off â†’ Security (pre-implementation)** before first code edit
- Load skills by intent: `.cursor/registry/skill-registry.yaml`, bundles `pre-feature`, `pre-implementation`
- Produce **Product Design Analysis** (Pillar 1) via `.cursor/skills/teknovo-ux-architecture/` or `.cursor/skills/teknovo-chief-product-designer/`
